# wexample-filestate-python

Helpers for Python.

Version: 0.0.42

## Requirements

- Python >=3.10

## Dependencies

- attrs>=23.1.0
- cattrs>=23.1.0
- wexample-filestate==0.0.52
- wexample-helpers-api==0.0.33

## Installation

```bash
pip install wexample-filestate-python
```

- Homepage: https://github.com/wexample/python-filestate-python
